casebody.data:
Jacob Romberg, appellant, v. Minnie Tobias, et al., respondents. Decided February 2, 1885. Appeal from order taxing costs. Wehle & Jordan, for appellant. Michael J. Kelly, and Joseph C. Wolff, for respondents.

Before Van Vorst and Freedman, JJ.

Per Curiam.

The order appealed from is affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements on the appeals.
